  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc8 15 \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u00a0 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0bbe",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel distribution at 15 fuel stations tomorrow in Jharkhand - here is the full details",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna District Secretary K. Mahesan has announced about the 15 fuel filling stations in Jaffna District that will be distributed to the public on Thursday.",
        "In addition to this, till the QR code is fully implemented, registrations will be made on the fuel supply card.",
        "1. Fuel can be purchased from any fuel station in addition to the fuel station specified in the fuel supply card using that card.",
        "Jaffna Multi-Purpose Cooperative Fuel Sales Station has been earmarked for essential needs.",
        "Due to this, the public is requested to get fuel from other fuel stations other than this fuel station.",
        "Further, diesel distribution will continue as usual through the Sri Lanka Transport Council to buses engaged in private transport and vehicles engaged in school services until further notice.",
        "The public should not wait in queues and follow the instructions published in the media to obtain fuel."
      ],
